{"thag2.19:0.1":"Theragatha 2.19 ","thag2.19:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.19:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag2.19:0.4":"Nandattheragatha ","thag2.19:1.1":"“Ayoniso manasikara, ","thag2.19:1.2":"mandanam anuyunjisam; ","thag2.19:1.3":"Uddhato capalo casim, ","thag2.19:1.4":"kamaragena attito. ","thag2.19:2.1":"Upayakusalenaham, ","thag2.19:2.2":"buddhenadiccabandhuna; ","thag2.19:2.3":"Yoniso patipajjitva, ","thag2.19:2.4":"bhave cittam udabbahin”ti. ","thag2.19:2.5":"… Nando thero …. "}